title: John Deere 's total assets 2013 to 2019
yAxis: Total assets in million U.S. dollars
summary: The chart at hand is a line chart where the x axis denotes Year and a y axis denotes Total assets in million U.S. dollars. In total the number of data points it has is 7.
Overall Total assets in million U.S. dollars has increased over the Year.
Total assets in million U.S. dollars is roughly constant from 2013 to 2016, and finally slightly increasing from 2016 to 2019.
The most drastic increase took place within the Year 2016 and 2017.
The highest Total assets in million U.S. dollars, of value 73011.0 was reached at Year 2019
The lowest Total assets in million U.S. dollars, of value 57947.6 was reported at Year 2015
